see

1152
00:54:31,830 --> 00:54:34,360
I hope you can express how you feel,

1153
00:54:36,810 --> 00:54:38,800
without hiding your true feelings,

1154
00:54:40,640 --> 00:54:41,800
like I did.

1155
00:54:42,570 --> 00:54:45,600
(If wishes could truly come true,)

1156
00:54:45,600 --> 00:54:48,950
(I’d like to repeat this life with you)

1157
00:54:48,950 --> 00:54:52,880
(Can it please be you?)

1158
00:54:52,880 --> 00:54:59,370
(No matter how far the road may be, it’s you I’ll always see)

1159
00:55:01,870 --> 00:55:03,400
Tomorrow, I’ll ask for leave.

1160
00:55:05,130 --> 00:55:07,800
Yu, can you call a ride?

1161
00:55:08,110 --> 00:55:09,210
They’re way too drunk.

1162
00:55:09,370 --> 00:55:09,980
Hey.

1163
00:55:10,520 --> 00:55:11,560
Who said I’m drunk?

1164
00:55:12,920 --> 00:55:15,250
I’m just not the same.

1165
00:55:16,250 --> 00:55:17,520
Pull yourself together.

1166
00:55:18,840 --> 00:55:20,430
The car is almost here.

1167
00:55:20,650 --> 00:55:21,980
It’s nearby.

1168
00:55:24,750 --> 00:55:25,510
Hey.

1169
00:55:25,510 --> 00:55:26,160
Huh?

1170
00:55:27,030 --> 00:55:28,250
I see grandma.

1171
00:55:29,520 --> 00:55:30,510
Where?

1172
00:55:30,510 --> 00:55:31,410
There.

1173
00:55:32,990 --> 00:55:33,980
Damn.

1174
00:55:34,310 --> 00:55:35,750
It’s not grandma.

1175
00:55:36,200 --> 00:55:37,560
It’s Mama noodles!

1176
00:55:38,210 --> 00:55:39,110
Yeah.

1177
00:55:39,110 --> 00:55:40,370
Whose car is this?

1178
00:55:41,010 --> 00:55:42,790
What should we do? This is a BMW.

1179
00:55:43,210 --> 00:55:44,840
Cutter, where are you going?

1180
00:55:46,870 --> 00:55:48,170
Well.

1181
00:55:48,590 --> 00:55:49,870
We need to find some water.

1182
00:55:49,870 --> 00:55:53,710
Before the owner comes after us.

1183
00:55:53,710 --> 00:55:54,650
Okay.

1184
00:56:05,250 --> 00:56:06,190
Here’s some water.

1185
00:56:08,110 --> 00:56:09,270
Thank you.

1186
00:56:11,980 --> 00:56:13,980
Cutter, come wash your face.

1187
00:56:15,230 --> 00:56:16,390
It’s not for him,

1188
00:56:17,330 --> 00:56:18,310
but the car.

1189
00:56:19,410 --> 00:56:22,370
Take some responsibility for throwing up at it.

1190
00:56:23,350 --> 00:56:25,760
He's old enough. Why doesn’t he know his limits?

1191
00:56:26,710 --> 00:56:28,350
Don't be a burden to others.

1192
00:56:28,350 --> 00:56:30,290
Sorry, my friend—

1193
00:56:30,290 --> 00:56:31,760
And you want to be an idol?

1194
00:56:32,250 --> 00:56:34,970
He can’t even set a good example for the younger generation.

1195
00:56:35,200 --> 00:56:36,270
Idol?

1196
00:56:37,350 --> 00:56:38,610
I want to be an idol.

1197
00:56:40,570 --> 00:56:42,610
He keeps shouting that loudly.

1198
00:56:44,210 --> 00:56:46,150
If you really want to be an idol,

1199
00:56:46,430 --> 00:56:48,110
use your mouth to practice singing

1200
00:56:49,200 --> 00:56:50,880
and dancing.

1201
00:56:51,770 --> 00:56:53,210
Calm down, please.

1202
00:56:53,210 --> 00:56:54,920
We’re Thai people. We’ve kind hearts.

1203
00:56:54,920 --> 00:56:56,920
Let’s be harmonious.

1204
00:56:56,920 --> 00:57:01,190
Let’s gather around and bring our hearts together.

1205
00:57:01,490 --> 00:57:02,680
No more harmony.

1206
00:57:04,870 --> 00:57:05,980
If I clean it, this ends here.

1207
00:57:07,560 --> 00:57:08,470
Fong.

1208
00:57:08,830 --> 00:57:10,210
Go check on Cutter.

1209
00:57:19,310 --> 00:57:21,090
Clean it properly.

1210
00:57:23,980 --> 00:57:25,200
Cutter, seriously.

1211
00:57:25,830 --> 00:57:27,070
Once you’re sober,

1212
00:57:27,600 --> 00:57:28,920
you’ll be punished.

1213
00:57:32,610 --> 00:57:33,980
Here, drink this.

1214
00:57:36,680 --> 00:57:38,410
You shouted a lot to help your friend.

1215
00:57:39,640 --> 00:57:41,160
Have some. It’ll soothe your throat.

1216
00:57:41,730 --> 00:57:43,080
You wanted to be an idol, right?

1217
00:57:44,400 --> 00:57:45,670
Take care of your voice.

1218
00:57:51,430 --> 00:57:52,840
You’re busy looking out for others.

1219
00:57:53,190 --> 00:57:54,730
Try looking after yourself too.

1220
00:58:18,550 --> 00:58:19,450
Keep wiping.

1221
00:58:32,490 --> 00:58:33,410
It’s clean now.

1222
00:58:33,670 --> 00:58:34,570
Are you satisfied?

1223
00:58:42,320 --> 00:58:43,270
Not bad.

1224
00:58:44,910 --> 00:58:47,480
Why do I feel like I’ve seen you before?

1225
00:58:48,750 --> 00:58:50,330
Have we met before?

1226
00:58:53,150 --> 00:58:54,130
I don’t think so.

1227
00:58:55,250 --> 00:58:57,680
Maybe we just passed by each other.

1228
00:58:59,390 --> 00:59:00,550
Passed by?

1229
00:59:01,530 --> 00:59:02,470
You look familiar.

1230
00:59:15,770 --> 00:59:16,950
You should go home.

1231
00:59:17,980 --> 00:59:18,930
Be good.

1232
00:59:26,090 --> 00:59:27,530
I’m sure we’ll meet again.

1233
00:59:32,840 --> 00:59:33,690
Can you move?

1234
00:59:33,690 --> 00:59:34,150
Oh!

1235
00:59:34,150 --> 00:59:34,960
I’m going home.

1236
00:59:34,960 --> 00:59:35,650
Okay.

1237
00:59:43,040 --> 00:59:44,600
Guys, move aside.

1238
01:00:08,770 --> 01:00:09,830
Hello, bro.

1239
01:00:13,190 --> 01:00:14,750
Alright, I’ll help you.

1240
01:00:19,240 --> 01:00:22,440
(Watch the uncut version only on iQIYI and IQ.com.)

